data.description: Don't miss out on this charming, ranch style home! This quiet HOA-free neighborhood is centrally located close (5min) to downtown, perfectly blending the peace and beauty of Colorado with all of the excitement Colorado Springs has to offer! With wide, bright windows and a covered porch, there are plenty of opportunities to enjoy clear sunny days, inside and out. This lot also has two storage sheds for all your outdoor gear, a privacy fence, and alley access for a future garage. The extra large master bedroom offers new vinyl plank flooring, and hardwood floors remain preserved beneath the carpet in the living and dining rooms. With an accessible ramp front entrance, this home offers main-floor living at its fullest!
